(extracted on 7 Mar 1999 from configshow-comments, default value is below)

# default_language
# (en)                 [string] <language>
# This sets the default language for the list (or the installation).
# This is overridable by the user in several ways.  Note that at this
# time this is barely implemented.  (Only English messages are supported
# at the moment.)
configset GLOBAL default_language = en

==> see also: configset     (for an overview and list of all variables)
==> see also: configedit    (to set the variable to a non-default value)
==> see also: configshow    (to display the variable's current value)
==> see also: configdefault (to have the variable track the default value)
==> see also: configset default_language (applies to regular lists also)

